act/153051/', '', 'Hydrochlorothiazide, Indapamide, Atorvastatin, Simvastatin, Lovastatin, Rosuvastatin, Pravastatin, Ezetimibe, Bempedoic acid, Indapamide, Fenofibrate', 'Ziconotide, Methoxyflurane', 1767369485);
